---
title: Easy Caribbean Beef Tacos with Cucumber Salsa & Mango Mayo
description: You told us you loved Jamaican jerk beef and we listened! We're giving it a spin in tasty tacos with rainbow salsa
and crunchy salad leaves to bring the meal together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-caribbean-beef-tacos-342441b4.jpg
